  "texts": [
    "Reflecting this growing interest and importance, 17 papers are classified under the \"Climate and Weather Monitoring\" category in our review.",
    "Among these papers, a small fraction include a mitigation component, likely because they inform long-term climate mitigation strategies (e.g., improving climate models for policy or clean energy production).",
